    {
      "kind": "content",
      "content": [
        {
          "anchor": "discussion",
          "level": 2,
          "text": "Discussion",
          "type": "heading"
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "To randomize the locations where new particles spawn, assign a geometry to this property. This geometry defines the shape of the space where new particles may spawn, and the "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": true,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/scenekit/scnparticlesystem/1522899-birthlocation"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " and "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": true,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/scenekit/scnparticlesystem/1523361-birthdirection"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " properties define locations within and directions relative to the shape. For example, assigning a sphere geometry causes particles to spawn at random locations along the surface of the sphere (or within the volume of the sphere, according to the "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": false,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/scenekit/scnparticlesystem/1522899-birthlocation"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " property). "
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "aside",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "inlineContent": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "For best results, use an instance of one of the SceneKit basic geometry classes ("
                },
                {
                  "type": "reference",
                  "isActive": true,
                  "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/scenekit/scnplane"
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": ", "
                },
                {
                  "type": "reference",
                  "isActive": true,
                  "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/scenekit/scnbox"
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": ", "
                },
                {
                  "type": "reference",
                  "isActive": true,
                  "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/scenekit/scnsphere"
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": ", "
                },
                {
                  "type": "reference",
                  "isActive": true,
                  "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/scenekit/scnpyramid"
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": ", "
                },
                {
                  "type": "reference",
                  "isActive": true,
                  "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/scenekit/scncone"
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": ", "
                },
                {
                  "type": "reference",
                  "isActive": true,
                  "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/scenekit/scncylinder"
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": ", "
                },
                {
                  "type": "reference",
                  "isActive": true,
                  "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/scenekit/scncapsule"
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": ", "
                },
                {
                  "type": "reference",
                  "isActive": true,
                  "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/scenekit/scntube"
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": ", and "
                },
                {
                  "type": "reference",
                  "isActive": true,
                  "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/scenekit/scntorus"
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "). These classes provide a more efficient simulation and more even appearance to the rendered particle system."
                }
              ]
            }
          ],
          "style": "note",
          "name": "Note"
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "The default value is "
            },
            {
              "type": "codeVoice",
              "code": "nil"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": ", specifying that all new particles emit from a single point. For particle systems attached to a node, this point is the origin of the nodeâs coordinate system. For particle systems attached directly to a scene using the "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": true,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/scenekit/scnscene/1523359-addparticlesystem"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " method, use that method's "
            },
            {
              "type": "codeVoice",
              "code": "transform"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " parameter to specify the emission point."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    }
